{"tid":2506563,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞飯TASTIC強勢回歸！全新Pikachu聯乘香蕉朱古力麥旋風/蘋果吉士批/白桃特飲登場！","createTime":"2021-04-27T11:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T11:42:57.000Z","uid":52127,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58ae567046803e0929d88bf39c17a5508ee629a0","tid":2506563,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"麥當勞今日宣佈，闊別已久的「飯TASTIC」終於在4月29日強勢回歸！是次「飯 TASTIC」將帶同兩款新口味登場，期間更聯乘Pok&eacute;mon推出一系列全新Pikachu造型限定美食，包括日本大熱的「蘋果吉士批」及「香蕉朱古力麥旋風」都旋風到港，即睇以下最新詳情啦！<br />\n<br />\n由 4月29日起，全新「汁燒牛肉飯 TASTIC」將打頭陣登場，而5月13日就將會有「吉列脆雞飯 TASTIC」接力登場，兩款「飯 TASTIC」均配上Pok&eacute;mon包裝盒，讓各位 Fans 一邊品嚐美食一邊打卡！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zaCCkuv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzaCCkuv.png&h=fdfc7677&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8aa77ede60de504c1242de388024ab8396a45d29","tid":2506563,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"麥當勞亦特意聯乘Pok&eacute;mon推出多款以Pikachu 造型為主題的全新美食！其中包括「惹味番茄調味粉」薯條，以及早前日本大熱的「蘋果吉士批」及「香蕉朱古力麥旋風」亦旋風登陸香港，「香蕉朱古力麥旋風」新地混合了香蕉果醬、朱古力醬和 Oreo 曲奇碎，對這款口味配搭有興趣的朋友，就千萬不能錯過喇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dXc65mY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdXc65mY.png&h=d7eefb7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oMOcuPG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoMOcuPG.png&h=0dd9317a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PURjQvj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPURjQvj.png&h=224b491c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8313b13526fbb7ec868d218bed9f99f10a1fca6","tid":2506563,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"即刻狗衝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b108251999488e6079303214aa